Enum TemporalHierarchy

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<TemporalHierarchy>
org.svvrl.goal.core.aut.fsa.TemporalHierarchy
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<TemporalHierarchy>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum TemporalHierarchy
extends java.lang.Enum<TemporalHierarchy>
This enumeration lists the classes in the Manna-Pnueli temporal hierarchy. Note that the order should be consistent with the order in the Büchi Store database.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
